initAfterJoin

protected void initAfterJoin()
                      throws hla.rti1516.RTIexception
This method is called from the ProxyAmbassador.joinFederationExecution(String, String, MobileFederateServices) method just after the federate has been joined. It is made sure that no callbacks from the RTI will be processed before this method has returned. Therefore, this method is the a suitable place to initialize HLA handles that need to be known when callbacks from the RTI are processed.

Specified by:
initAfterJoin in class org.eodisp.wrapper.hla.ProxyAmbassador
Throws:
hla.rti1516.RTIexception
